    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offered is a mechanically sound E46 M3 featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six engine. This power plant utilizes six individual throttle bodies and a double-VANOS variable valve timing system that has been meticulously serviced for optimal torque delivery. Power is routed through a Getrag six-speed manual transmission to a limited-slip differential. The chassis benefits from reinforced rear subframe mounting points, addressing a known platform weakness, and the suspension retains its factory-spec MacPherson strut front and multi-link rear geometry. Recent valve clearance adjustments and fresh bushings ensure the vehicle maintains its signature handling precision and linear power delivery. A true driver's example with a solid mechanical foundation.",
