    {
      "id": "sybil_9_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_9",
      "description": "Up for sale is a meticulously maintained vehicle that strikes the perfect balance between luxury and daily reliability. The exterior retains a brilliant luster, though close inspection reveals a few minor stone chips on the front fascia\u2014honest evidence of enjoyable highway miles. Inside, the cabin remains a sanctuary; the premium leather upholstery is free of tears, showing only light, natural creasing on the driver\u2019s side bolster. Every feature, from the dual-zone climate control to the responsive touchscreen infotainment system, functions exactly as intended. Mechanically, this car is in its prime. It has been serviced strictly according to the manufacturer\u2019s schedule, featuring a smooth-shifting transmission and a quiet, powerful engine that has never missed a beat. The tires offer deep tread for the seasons ahead, and the brakes provide confident, firm stopping power. This is a smoke-free, pet-free vehicle that has been garage-kept and consistently detailed. It\u2019s ready for its next owner to drive away with complete peace of mind.",
      "price": 36800.0,
