    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "This 2008 Porsche Cayman S features the mid-mounted 3.4L flat-six M97 engine, delivering linear power through a precise 6-speed manual transaxle. The chassis remains taut, benefiting from a MacPherson strut arrangement and staggered alloy wheels that provide exceptional lateral grip and communicative steering feedback. Mechanically sound, the vehicle maintains consistent oil pressure and has undergone a recent borescope inspection to ensure cylinder wall integrity. The braking system utilizes four-piston monobloc aluminum calipers over cross-drilled rotors, offering firm pedal feel and minimal fade. This example is an ideal driver-spec machine for those prioritizing mechanical purity and the balanced polar moment of inertia inherent to the 987 platform. Recent service includes a fresh drive belt and a comprehensive fluid flush.",
